Global 2-Ethylhexanoyl Chloride(CAS 760-67-8) Market Insights
2-Ethylhexanoyl Chloride(CAS 760-67-8) Market size was valued at USD 0.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.25 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8% from 2024 to 2030.

2-Ethylhexanoyl Chloride(CAS 760-67-8) Market Overview
The global market for 2-Ethylhexanoyl Chloride (CAS 760-67-8) has seen consistent growth driven by its increasing demand in various industries such as plasticizers, paints, and coatings, among others. The market value in 2024 was estimated at USD 500 million and is expected to grow at a CAGR of approximately 4.5% through 2030. The compound is widely used as an intermediate in the synthesis of plasticizers and stabilizers, contributing to its market expansion. With increasing industrialization, the demand for 2-Ethylhexanoyl Chloride continues to rise, particularly in Asia-Pacific regions, where manufacturing hubs are situated. The market is also being influenced by advancements in chemical manufacturing processes and sustainable production techniques. However, fluctuations in raw material prices and environmental concerns related to the production of certain chemicals are posing challenges to the growth trajectory. The increasing awareness of green and sustainable chemicals will play a significant role in the market's evolution moving forward.

